                            <comment id="16642314" author="gerlowskija" created="Mon, 8 Oct 2018 18:56:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch replaces the reference to &lt;tt&gt;CloudSolrClient.uploadConfig&lt;/tt&gt; with a small SolrJ snippet showing how to use ZkStateManager to upload configsets.  The snippet is pulled in from a JUnit test using asciidoc&apos;s &quot;include&quot; syntax, so it should stay up to date if anything happens to those interfaces in the future.&lt;/p&gt;

